    <p class="cordyceps-text">A study published in <strong>Nutrients (2023)</strong> found that <strong>Cordyceps militaris</strong> supplementation improves aerobic performance and energy metabolism by enhancing ATP production, making it beneficial for athletes and active individuals.</p>

